&lt;p data-start=&quot;227&quot; data-end=&quot;307&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;227&quot; data-end=&quot;236&quot;&gt;ROLE:&lt;/strong&gt; Account Director&lt;br data-start=&quot;253&quot; data-end=&quot;256&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;256&quot; data-end=&quot;265&quot;&gt;TEAM:&lt;/strong&gt; Accounts&lt;br data-start=&quot;274&quot; data-end=&quot;277&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;277&quot; data-end=&quot;290&quot;&gt;LOCATION:&lt;/strong&gt; Toronto (Hybrid)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;309&quot; data-end=&quot;329&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;309&quot; data-end=&quot;329&quot;&gt;COMPANY OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;331&quot; data-end=&quot;710&quot;&gt;Salt is a North American marketing agency that creates connected experiences through creative, digital, and media innovation. Our mission is to help clients, and their brands earn the world’s attention through our core philosophy of &lt;strong data-start=&quot;564&quot; data-end=&quot;588&quot;&gt;Connected Creativity&lt;/strong&gt; - a cross-disciplinary, collaborative approach to ideation and planning that unlocks the power of different perspectives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;712&quot; data-end=&quot;829&quot;&gt;This approach enables us to deliver new and effective solutions. Because the best results start with different ideas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;831&quot; data-end=&quot;848&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;831&quot; data-end=&quot;848&quot;&gt;ROLE OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;850&quot; data-end=&quot;1165&quot;&gt;As an Account Director, you’ll lead a portfolio of integrated campaigns from strategy through execution, acting as the central driver of both client relationships and internal team performance. You’ll serve as the general manager of your business—owning delivery, growth, and team alignment across every touchpoint.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1167&quot; data-end=&quot;1462&quot;&gt;You’ll oversee cross-functional teams, guiding the development of programs that are insight-led, creatively sharp, and built to perform. From setting the vision to briefing creative, managing timelines, and owning the budget, you’ll keep the work on track and the client confident in every step.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1464&quot; data-end=&quot;1698&quot;&gt;This role is for a strategic thinker and hands-on leader. You know how to turn complexity into clarity and move ideas into action. You’re a strong communicator, a collaborative partner, and a steady force in a fast-moving environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1700&quot; data-end=&quot;1725&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1700&quot; data-end=&quot;1725&quot;&gt;CORE RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1727&quot; data-end=&quot;1747&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1727&quot; data-end=&quot;1747&quot;&gt;Client Relations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1749&quot; data-end=&quot;2342&quot;&gt;• Develop and deepen trusted client relationships, acting as a strategic advisor aligned to business goals and brand objectives.&lt;br data-start=&quot;1877&quot; data-end=&quot;1880&quot;&gt;• Lead the development and execution of integrated marketing (IMC) programs, ensuring excellence from concept to delivery.&lt;br data-start=&quot;2002&quot; data-end=&quot;2005&quot;&gt;• Maintain a strong understanding of the client’s business, industry landscape, and growth drivers.&lt;br data-start=&quot;2104&quot; data-end=&quot;2107&quot;&gt;• Identify and pursue opportunities for organic account growth by proposing incremental programs and value-added services.&lt;br data-start=&quot;2229&quot; data-end=&quot;2232&quot;&gt;• Provide strategic brand and business guidance to clients as needed, fostering long-term partnership success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2344&quot; data-end=&quot;2352&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2344&quot; data-end=&quot;235

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;POSITION DESCRIPTION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;ROLE: ACCOUNT&amp;nbsp;FIELD&amp;nbsp;COORDINATOR&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;TEAM: ACCOUNTS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;LOCATION: CALGARY, ALBERTA&lt;br&gt;ROLE: CONTRACT - END OF DECEMBER&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;COMPANY OVERVIEW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Salt is a North American marketing agency that creates connected experiences through creative, digital &amp;amp; media innovation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Our mission is to “Earn The World’s Attention” and Salt is built to find, develop, execute, and amplify the ideas that are worthy of our clients’ audiences. We’ve structured our agency to do what’s right for our clients – to connect different perspectives, to work across mediums, and to focus on delivering meaningful, effective results.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We’re&amp;nbsp;committed to living up to the values in our name. “Salt of The Earth” means we value collaborative, humble, hard-working people here.&amp;nbsp;We’re&amp;nbsp;looking for people who are as smart as they are kind because we believe the right talent and the right culture help us do what’s right for our clients.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;ROLE OVERVIEW&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We&#39;re&amp;nbsp;looking for an In-Field Coordinator to be on the ground at experiential events across the&amp;nbsp;province .&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll&amp;nbsp;work directly alongside our team of brand ambassadors, owning the operational details that make events run smoothly—from setup through execution to tear-down. This is a hands-on role for someone who thrives in motion and brings energy to every activation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335557856&amp;quot;:16777215,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
