&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Group Strategy Director&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;is a leadership role within The Kitchen -Kraft Heinz’s integrated creative function- uniquely embedded into the Kraft Heinz business, responsible for driving strategic excellence across a designated business unit comprising 4-8 consumer-facing brands. This individual will serve as a strategic consult for their business unit, connecting brand objectives to actionable insights and creative direction for The Kitchen. Reporting to the Head of Strategy in The Kitchen, the Group Strategy Director will lead a team of strategists, collaborate with creative and communication leads, and act as a strategic partner to senior marketing leadership within their business unit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
