&lt;li&gt;Lead the strategic planning process for your assigned brands in The Kitchen, identifying opportunities for growth, innovation, and market differentiation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn these brands, inside and out. Provide thought leadership to help elevate brand positioning, messaging, and consumer engagement strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help develop and maintain the long-term creative strategic vision for the business unit, ensuring alignment with overarching company objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary strategic partner for Brand Communication and General Manager counterparts, ensuring alignment across creative, as well as owned, earned, and paid media channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Embed into the business’ standing meetings and routines to ensure 360 understanding of the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate closely with creative, insights, and analytics teams to translate data into actionable strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the voice of creative strategy in senior-level business unit meetings, representing The Kitchen with professionalism and expertise.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Management&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage and mentor a team of Pod Strategists and Social Managers within The Kitchen, contributing to a culture of collaboration, creativity and high performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure integration and understanding of strategic insights into creative briefs and campaign planning across Kitchen work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability by setting clear goals, performance metrics, and professional development plans for Kitchen team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consumer Insights &amp;amp; Market Trends&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay ahead of market trends, cultural shifts, and consumer behavior to proactively inform brand strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Consumer Insights specialists to leverage research and analytics in building data-driven strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and capitalize on emerging opportunities for the business unit’s portfolio of brands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
