&lt;p data-start=&quot;152&quot; data-end=&quot;205&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;152&quot; data-end=&quot;203&quot;&gt;ROLE: INTEGRATED MEDIA BUYING MANAGER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;207&quot; data-end=&quot;244&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;207&quot; data-end=&quot;242&quot;&gt;TEAM: CRAFT &amp;amp; COMMERCE - MEDIA OPERATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;246&quot; data-end=&quot;294&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;246&quot; data-end=&quot;292&quot;&gt;LOCATION: UNITED STATES - REMOTE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT CRAFT &amp;amp; COMMERCE&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Craft &amp;amp; Commerce (C&amp;amp;C) is an integrated media agency, purpose-built to serve as a nimble, strategic partner to marketing teams in navigating our rapidly evolving media landscape. We fuse leading-edge performance marketing capabilities with a holistic view of channels, bring clarity to measurement and attribution across the funnel, and deliver scalable, ad-driven growth. Our expert team has stood in the shoes of our clients and sees media through the lens of larger business objectives. We combine this human touch with best-in-class technology and a suite of services focused on one thing: continually driving better results through media.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for an &lt;strong&gt;Integrated Media Buying Manager&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to strategize, execute, optimize and report upon successful paid advertising campaigns effectively for our partners, across CPG, healthcare, nonprofit, technology and other industries.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Integrated Media Buying Manager will be an integral part of our fast-growing, collaborative, and entrepreneurial team. We will look to you to assist us in developing and executing media buys for our partners. The role entails planning, executing, optimizing, and reporting on advertising campaigns across platforms and media for multiple concurrent clients. The ideal candidate will be a highly detailed, analytical, and solutions-oriented team player with strong relationship-building and communication skills. If you are driven by achieving results for clients and are known to go above and beyond to maintain high standards in your work, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And—at C&amp;amp;C—we treasure a candid, ask-the-right-questions, get-it-done attitude that’s at the heart of our fast-moving and collaborative team culture. We’re a flexible, balanced, self-driven workplace. The right candidate will join us remotely from a place that makes you happy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CORE RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee and execute campaigns across various media platforms including Meta, X, TikTok, LinkedIn, Reddit, Google Ads, Bing Ads, DSPs (StackAdapt), Retail Media Networks, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet with partners, prepare plans for media, organize budgets, and negotiate the costs of advertising with vendors when applicable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow current market trends and understand our clients’ target consumer patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an advocate for new systems and tools to continuously expand our advertising capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works collaboratively as an enthusiastic advocate for our clients’ paid media campaigns and budgets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with creative teams in directing content creation to ensure accurate specs and tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set up new ads within various social / digital platforms&lt;/li&

