&lt;h4&gt;ROLE: MEDIA ACTIVATION SPECIALIST&lt;br&gt;TEAM: MEDIA&lt;br&gt;LOCATION: TORONTO (HYBRID ONSITE)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;COMPANY OVERVIEW&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Salt is a North American marketing agency that creates connected experiences through creative, digital &amp;amp; media innovation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our mission is to “Earn the World’s Attention,” and Salt is built to find, develop, execute, and amplify the ideas that matter to our clients’ audiences. We are structured to do what’s right for our clients — connecting perspectives,&amp;nbsp;operating&amp;nbsp;across mediums, and ensuring meaningful, effective creative solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We live the values in our name. “Salt of the Earth” reflects how we work: collaborative, humble, and hard-working. We believe talent and culture create&amp;nbsp;great work&amp;nbsp;— so&amp;nbsp;we&#39;re&amp;nbsp;looking for people who are as smart as they are kind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;ROLE OVERVIEW&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Activation Specialist &lt;/strong&gt;will work across an exciting mix of US clients across different industries, providing day-to-day support to the wider media team, with a focus on activation and optimization of digital channels.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need to be highly proficient in media implementation, the digital media landscape, and performance marketing. This includes a strong understanding of social media platforms, programmatic channels, Google Analytics, and vendor management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will develop strong trust-based relationships with both clients and agency team members. Curiosity and common sense are essential to staying up to date on platform and partner capabilities and identifying opportunities for clients and the broader team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;CORE RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with the team to support implementation, optimization, and reporting for key clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with the team to assist with overall client planning and day-to-day client requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work directly with media partners to book, implement, and report on campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the preparation, writing, and presentation of integrated media plans, proposals, and analyses that satisfy client objectives and go beyond the brief.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain stewardship and accountability of media plans, regularly evaluating and monitoring execution to implement meaningful optimizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise and foster knowledge sharing with other disciplines internally, partner agencies, and departments to ensure media and client knowledge remains current.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all media plans adhere to the agency&#39;s values, philosophies, and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute ideas and opinions on clients&#39; businesses, agency operations, and industry trends; establish a presence within the agency and contribute in meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain awareness of client KPIs and objectives, ensuring tracking is in place for regular check-ins.&lt;/li&gt;
