&lt;p data-start=&quot;529&quot; data-end=&quot;675&quot;&gt;Company Overview&lt;br data-start=&quot;545&quot; data-end=&quot;548&quot;&gt;Salt is a North American marketing agency that creates connected experiences through creative, digital, and media innovation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;677&quot; data-end=&quot;949&quot;&gt;Our mission is to “Earn the World’s Attention.” We are built to find, develop, execute, and amplify ideas that resonate with our clients’ audiences. We are structured to connect perspectives, work across mediums, and focus on delivering meaningful and effective results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;951&quot; data-end=&quot;1098&quot;&gt;We value people who are collaborative, humble, and hardworking. We believe the right talent and culture help us do what is right for our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1100&quot; data-end=&quot;1373&quot;&gt;Role Overview&lt;br data-start=&quot;1113&quot; data-end=&quot;1116&quot;&gt;Salt is seeking a results driven Sales Representative to represent a leading tech client within a retail environment at Best Buy. This role is ideal for someone passionate about technology, confident in sales, and comfortable in a customer facing setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1375&quot; data-end=&quot;1458&quot;&gt;This role is scheduled Thursday through Sunday each week for a total of 20 hours.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1460&quot; data-end=&quot;1792&quot;&gt;As a Sales Representative, you will be responsible for driving product sales, maintaining strong retail relationships, and ensuring in store presence is executed to the highest standard. You will act as a brand expert, educating customers while supporting retail partners through strong communication, organization, and execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1794&quot; data-end=&quot;1944&quot;&gt;This position requires a self motivated professional who can work independently, build rapport quickly, and consistently deliver measurable results.&lt;/p&gt;
