&lt;h4&gt;ROLE: SEM SUPERVISOR&lt;br&gt;TEAM: MEDIA&lt;br&gt;LOCATION: TORONTO (HYBRID ONSITE)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;COMPANY OVERVIEW&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Salt is a North American marketing agency that creates connected experiences through creative, digital &amp;amp; media innovation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Our mission is to “Earn the World’s Attention,” and Salt is built to find, develop, execute, and amplify the ideas that matter to our clients’ audiences. We are structured to do what’s right for our clients — connecting perspectives,&amp;nbsp;operating&amp;nbsp;across mediums, and ensuring meaningful, effective creative solutions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We live the values in our name. “Salt of the Earth” reflects how we work: collaborative, humble, and hard-working. We believe talent and culture create&amp;nbsp;great work&amp;nbsp;— so&amp;nbsp;we&#39;re&amp;nbsp;looking for people who are as smart as they are kind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;ROLE OVERVIEW&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s15&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;As an &lt;strong&gt;SEM Supervisor&lt;/strong&gt;, you will lead the strategic planning, execution, and optimization of search and retail media programs across a portfolio of clients while providing day-to-day leadership to members of the SEM team. You&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;are responsible for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;delivering integrated, data-driven media strategies that drive measurable business outcomes while ensuring campaigns are executed efficiently, governed effectively, and&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;in accordance with&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;best practices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s16&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;You will act as the senior subject matter expert across search and retail media, providing strategic recommendations to clients, mentoring team members, and championing continuous improvement through analytics, testing, and platform innovation. Just as importantly, you will translate complex platform capabilities and performance insights into clear, actionable recommendations for clients and internal stakeholders, helping them understand how search contributes to broader business and media objectives. Working closely with Client Services, Strategy, Analytics, and Creative teams, you will shape integrated media solutions while supporting the operational excellence required to manage high-performing search programs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;s16&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s14&quot;&gt;This role balances hands-on expertise with people leadership and is responsible for elevating team capability, strengthening client relationships, driving operational excellence across account administration and governance, and contributing to the ongoing evolution of Salt’s performance media practice.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&

