&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead full-cycle recruitment across field sales, corporate, and program roles nationally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own hiring strategy for high-volume, specialized, and hard-to-fill roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Encore leadership to forecast workforce needs aligned to growth plans and client programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead intake sessions to define competencies, success profiles, and assessment approaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scalable hiring strategies including talent pooling, streamlined assessment processes, and strategic use of external recruitment partners to ensure speed, quality, and cost-effectiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain proactive talent pipelines across key markets and functions.&lt;/li&gt;
